        "title": "Port + Graph Reference Demo",
        "purpose": "Ports consume a view from a target graph (node.web.* surfaces only). Graph Reference nodes preview/embed a target graph.\n\nUse the edit drawer to switch the consumed view and ensure it stays hydrated and deterministic.",
