    {
      "id": "port-ref-demo-instructions",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Instructions",
      "position": { "x": -260, "y": 40 },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 360,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Try it\n\n### Consuming port\n1) Click the port node.\n2) In the drawer, change **View** between `node.web.summary` and `node.web.detail`.\n3) Confirm the consumed rendering updates and the dropdown stays stable.\n\n### Preview port\n1) Click the preview port.\n2) Confirm it renders minimap from only the address.\n\nExpected:\n- Port view list is deterministic\n- Port renders minimap fallback when target has no matching surface\n- Preview rendering is stable"
      }
    },
